{"tid":1234302,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候比廢老知道，普選/投票，先係治標放法","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T14:22:50.000Z","uid":107562,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"33e16e502dbd5bd605fa0d481cae3967cc7ca62a","tid":1234302,"uid":107562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:33:25.000Z","msg":"其實現在的情況好不妙，希望大家有危機意識。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭鳩up句sor，降溫，一定會有部份人會得佢已經道左歉，而家佔領金鐘果班係搞事，星期日我相信有好多人係因為見到警察打人開槍，先行出來（雞蛋和高牆，我永遠站係雞蛋一方）但係警察最新策略係你鍾意行邊都得唔阻你。港豬亦都會覺得，件事已經完咗，點解仲要左人返工放工。咁我地仲可以做咩？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以整新的長者圖，提醒善忘嘅香港人<br />\n1.林鄭沒冇回應訴求<br />\n2.沒有普選，只係換煲不換藥，林鄭2.0<br />\n3.記得投票，不要再投，工黨，民建聯，新民黨"},{"pid":"943e5a80a42ea9ccd6e0700d72ab5ce27614a547","tid":1234302,"uid":107562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:34:41.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"575d785883a1ed27cfde55d627a022ecaf74e14a","tid":1234302,"uid":139156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"有著數咪投你一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無著數仲想同我講政治？<br />\n收皮啦！"},{"pid":"980827ea1ef2937c18229a88bca822848fc83947","tid":1234302,"uid":107562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cb78f56cd3218bd8ba980f70778ef10a276b0a4","tid":1234302,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:35:30.000Z","msg":"香港就嚟輸，想贏就要有下一步<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234257\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234257</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd287c5a0550d93932e97b11f71c5806a3f69510","tid":1234302,"uid":107562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2d54a0536245fa2f6e328666f26427ef59b5252","tid":1234302,"uid":107562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdc455d60fdc45e3219891b11718e6aa39619fef","tid":1234302,"uid":107